description: Number of partitions of n into parts not of the form 25k, 25k+4 or 25k-4. Also number of partitions with at most 3 parts of size 1 and differences between parts at distance 11 are greater than 1.
references: G. E. Andrews, The Theory of Partitions, Addison-Wesley, 1976, p. 109.
